Build : 
  Step 1 : 
    New Item : maven_web_build
    Freestyle
  Step 2 : 
    Description : Maven Web Build Demo
    Git : Maven Java : https://github.com/AnishaPaturi/Maven_Web.git
    Branch -> main
  Step 3 : Build 
    Invoke top-level Maven targets 
      clean 
      install
  Step 4 : Post Build
    Archive the artifacts : **/*
    Build on other projetcs : maven_web_build
  Step 5 : Apply and save 
    Build now

Test : 
  Step 1 : 
      New Item : maven_web_test
      Freestyle
    Step 2 : 
      Description : Maven Web Test Demo
      none 
      Delete Workspace 
    Step 3 : Build 
      Invoke top-level Maven targets :
        test 
      Copy artifacts from another project : 
        maven_web_build
        **/*
    Step 4 : Post Build
      Archive the artifacts : **/*
      Build on other projetcs : maven_web_build
    Step 5 : Apply and save 
      Build now

Deploy : 
  Step 1 : 
      New Item : maven_web_depoy
      Freestyle
    Step 2 : 
      Description : Maven Web Deploy Demo
      none 
      Delete Workspace 
    Step 3 : Build 
      Copy artifacts from another project : 
        maven_web_test
        **/*
    Step 4 : Post Build
      Deploy war/ear to a container
        WAR/EAR files : **/*.war
        context path : webpath 
        Container : new 
          Credentials : Tomcat Manager 
          [ win + R : cmd 
            tomcat/apcahe/bin/startup.bat -----> To see the port number ]
{
  Jenkins manager -> Credentials -> global -> Add -> username : admin ; password : admin ; ID : tomcat-creds -> save 
  tomcat/conf/cmd -> notepad tomcat-users.xml : 
  <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
  <tomcat-users>
  
      <!-- Roles needed for Jenkins automation deployments -->
      <role rolename="manager-script"/>
      <role rolename="manager-status"/>
  
      <!-- DO NOT ADD manager-gui or manager-jmx for Jenkins -->
      <user username="admin" password="admin" roles="manager-script,manager-status"/>
  
  </tomcat-users>
}
    Step 5 : Apply and save 
      Build now
In the browser open http://localhost:<port number of tomcat>/webpath
